modDescription:
Make ordinary bandage can also restore a small amount of health, not to let you helpless. And it can provide the upper stacking limit of [medical](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-medical-supplies/) consumables.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1NtKr4pWUhxiRdc1_k1IindvVUBmHr5ik)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/22921-a19bbbbillys-practical-mods-collection/).
